<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Probably after about 3 hours a day for about 2 weeks sitting at the ruins after school she finally spawned for me. there she was just standing at the left corner of the arcway in the ruins when i finally noticed she was there. so me being a level 16 warrior at the time figured i could take her down pretty easily she coned blue and her pet was green went after her first and BAM dots stacked up faster then pamala anderson and i was down to half life before i started to hit her.then she feared me and finally when i broke the fear i was at one bubble. she then took a tough beating from me and she went to half life and finally i died.<BR>
So i ran back to get my corpse as fast as i could and she was standing right on top of it. I summoned it to me got my stuff and layed the smackdown on her one last time and finally killed her. bouncing up and down in my seat i proceed to loot her corpse. did i get the GBS? NO I GOT A RUSTY DAGGER! A GODDAMN RUSTY DAGGER! WHAT THE %&!# IS WRONG WITH THIS PICTURE! I LOSE A HALF A BUBBLE OF EXP AND 3 WEEKS OF MY LIFE FOR A RUSTY DAGGER?! *chews on some prozac* Ahhh i fell a much better now. where was i again? oh yes a rusty dagger. good luck with this b*tch and have a nice day. 8p </font></td></tr></table>
