<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Brinks of Povar</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-25 18:32:49</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Ok here is my story. one day about a month ago i decided to camp pyzjn. I checked all the sites i could gathering info, logged in and talked to many other ppl getting more info.i went to Qhills zone and to the skell ruins. it was daytime, from what others told me, she only spawned at night( an EQ night is from 6pm -6am). i decided to stay as long as i could stay up...i killed everything i saw. skells, rats, bats, dread skells,wolfs, mangy rats, snakes, fire beetles. as i was camping many others came and went..of every class and lvl. they gave me all kinds of info and "hints". some made sense others did not. they say tovax is a PH and varsoon is a PH and mangy rats ect. ect. But, the most common thing that was said that she only comes at night. which i think we all agree on. my frist day there i spent 25 hours straight, killing everything. i saw her one time at 2am game time she poped in the middle of the ruins..no stone. had to sleep. came back on line the next day, 20 hours straight killed her 3 times all between 12am and 4 am, all 3 times she wandered from the hills toward moving towards the ruins. one time she spawned i know for sure tovax was up...my friend had him on trac...so tovax is NOT a PH. 45 hours so far nothing. for the next 2 WEEKS i spent 5 hours a day on weekdays and 20 hours on weekends. over that time she spawed 11 more times. NO stone so a total of 15 spawns and no stone. she came from the hills a total of 9 times and poped at the ruins 6 times ( in a few different places) After well over 250 hours of total RL camp time i gave up. leaving with no stone. then about a week later i logged in and was gonna go to Lguk when i saw the sun setting. did a /time and it said 7 pm..so i decided to go there( was stil bound there) stood around not killing anything only myself and a lvl 5 monk in the zone. and then at 1 am gametime there she was strolling down the hill..i was like whoopie! another rusty dagger!..i went and killed her for the 16th time..and there it was a rusty dagger. followed by a black pearl looking item) i jumped outa my chair in disbelief, looted it and put it on...i was so happy. i finally got it! now think of the situation...im not killing anything, the lvl 5 monk was on the other side of the zone. maybe someone just zoned out after kiling something, right b4 i zoned in,,who knows,,but the ruins were full and i didnt kill a thing. after i got i decided to do something smart...for all of you that think the spell i dentify is usless check this out. i casted it on the GBS and this is what it said " heart of varsoon" so after seeing that i came up with the conclusion that varsoon is a PH . im still not sure how to make her pop. you just have to bind there and stay the nights. its just a matter of luck=) i hope you liked my story and the info from it. Have fun and good Hunting.<BR>
<BR>
Brinks of Povar lvl 49 wizard ( with a GBS!)</font></td></tr></table>
