<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>OK out of all the storys ive read on this page it seems that everyonr thinks Tovax and Varsoon are place holders, well that doesn't seem to be true. Well for 1.I was camping pyjzn with a lvl 27 ranger friend (me lvl 12 enchanter) she said that Tovax had poped on her tracking scope so i had her lead me to him and i rooted and nuked him in 3 kills with my animation on his pet he was rather easy (he droped rusty dagger) after that we ran back to ruins and still no pyjzn. ok 2. I was there the other night (6-29-00) and a lvl 40 enchanter friend and a lvl 49 wizard friend where camping her and i was sitting in the middle of the ruins medding when all of a sudden i saw on my chat screen "pyjzn begins to cast a spell" so i jumped up with only about 50 mana left hit her with a DD spell and took her to half life and by then the wizard and the enhcnater where all over her like Holly on someone killing a bear or wolf i ended getting enough damage and not have them KS (made them so mad) so i looted it and just a damn rusty dagger ok now to 3. Ive heard about a quest where you follow tovax for a while and he walks to the ruins then drops a note and if you pick it up Varsoon will spawn (still not confirmed) so i followed Tovax all the way to the ruins and he drop the note and i picked it up and then Tovax ran non-stop back to his spawn point where i killed him then i heard someone shout "ACK !!Varsoon at the ruins run for your lives!!" at that point i gated back to the ruins where and landed right on top of Varson and he killed me rather quick so when i re-spawned on my corpse he was gone ok now to 4. i campd him a week ago and pyjzn spawned TWICE in the same night first she spawned right in the middle of the ruins with 2 dreads, 1 putrid, and her pet she was blue con (im 12th lvl enchanter) so i went at her not relizing that the dreads would come and kill me i died pretty fast and when i came back she was gone (no one killed her i was only person in the zone, not counting the NPC's) so i have come to believe that if you don't kill her she will run to the guards and they will kill her. and also that if you follow tova to the ruins and pick up the note he drops and let him live either Varsoon, Pyjzn, or a mangy rat will spawn so if you have some time while caping pyjzn and you hear someone say tovax up shout out and tell everyone not to kill him hes for a quest and follow him untill he drops the note, pick it up, and stick around the ruins and see what spawns its worth a try <BR>
Deinia 12th lvl enchanter off Povar </font></td></tr></table>
